<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>اللَّهَ عَلَيْهِ﴾ <span class="c2">(١)</span> الْآيَةَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>هَذَا حَدِيثٌ صَحِيحُ الْإِسْنَادِ، وَلَمْ يُخَرِّجَاهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
